listing_name: The Farm Market at Mill No. 5
location_desc: The Farm Market typically operates indoors, year-round at Mill No. 5 as a destination for community gathering. The market has moved outdoors when possible because of Covid19. Please check for our status each week. The market emphasizes a direct connection between producer and consumer with the purpose of supporting local food producers, building the local food economy, and increasing food access.
